{{>header}}
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <img src="https://your-cdn.com/logo.png" alt="Homnifi Logo">
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear {{customerName}},</p>
        <h1>Welcome to Homnifi!</h1>
        <p>We are delighted to welcome you to Homnifi, where the future of Web3 and decentralized finance comes to life. You are now part of an evolving ecosystem designed to empower you with cutting-edge tools and resources to optimize your digital experience.</p>
